items.title: Informatica to Report Second Quarter 2025 Financial Results on August 6, 2025
items.description: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., July 16, 2025--Informatica (NYSE: INFA), an AI-powered enterprise cloud data management leader, today announced it will report financial results for the second quarter 2025, which ended June 30, 2025, following the close of the U.S. markets on Wednesday, August 6, 2025.

items.title: Backstroke Lands $2.8M, New Executive Talent, and Announces Upgraded Features Amid AI Marketing Boom
items.description: INDIANAPOLIS, July 16, 2025--Backstroke, the generative AI email marketing platform for e-commerce brands, today announced $2.8 million in new growth funding led by Allos Ventures, with continued participation from High Alpha and Ground Game Ventures. Year-over-year growth from June 2024 to June 2025 reached an impressive 375% in customer count and 447% in annual recurring revenue (ARR).
